org.alicebot.ab

Class Chat

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.alicebot.ab.Chat

  • public class Chat
extends java.lang.Object
    Primary class for creating a Chat interface between a Bot and a user. This class essentially is the interface between the users input and the Bot's datasets.
    Author:
    Dave
